  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3b5d86633acee96645aa9233a5936f56.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong><i>Choose your gear wisely and make it from shelter to shelter. Your mood plays an important role in your survival. Pick up airdrops or cut down trees to get loot. Be careful of traps, rough weather conditions and wild animals that attack you. Hike on tons of procedural generated \"real-world GPX\" or fantasy trails.</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Competition</strong></h2><i>Enjoy playing against computer or human controlled hikers.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/16d48e80ab415cf8f50f270cff4c90d1.poster.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/16d48e80ab415cf8f50f270cff4c90d1.webm?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/16d48e80ab415cf8f50f270cff4c90d1.mp4?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock Inventory</strong></h2><i>Give your rucksack a new style with badges and make your character unique with a variety of hats.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3f5020aa4bdc7e6ad3e233dd3dab9ba0.poster.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3f5020aa4bdc7e6ad3e233dd3dab9ba0.webm?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3f5020aa4bdc7e6ad3e233dd3dab9ba0.mp4?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Editor</strong></h2><i>Create unique trails yourself or import GPX files.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/cd1b7a1a575f6c03b1bfc63c606e427e.poster.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/cd1b7a1a575f6c03b1bfc63c606e427e.webm?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/cd1b7a1a575f6c03b1bfc63c606e427e.mp4?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3b5d86633acee96645aa9233a5936f56.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong><i>Choose your gear wisely and make it from shelter to shelter. Your mood plays an important role in your survival. Pick up airdrops or cut down trees to get loot. Be careful of traps, rough weather conditions and wild animals that attack you. Hike on tons of procedural generated \"real-world GPX\" or fantasy trails.</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Competition</strong></h2><i>Enjoy playing against computer or human controlled hikers.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/16d48e80ab415cf8f50f270cff4c90d1.poster.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/16d48e80ab415cf8f50f270cff4c90d1.webm?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/16d48e80ab415cf8f50f270cff4c90d1.mp4?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock Inventory</strong></h2><i>Give your rucksack a new style with badges and make your character unique with a variety of hats.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3f5020aa4bdc7e6ad3e233dd3dab9ba0.poster.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3f5020aa4bdc7e6ad3e233dd3dab9ba0.webm?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/3f5020aa4bdc7e6ad3e233dd3dab9ba0.mp4?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Editor</strong></h2><i>Create unique trails yourself or import GPX files.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/cd1b7a1a575f6c03b1bfc63c606e427e.poster.avif?t=1596293150\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/cd1b7a1a575f6c03b1bfc63c606e427e.webm?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/722290/extras/cd1b7a1a575f6c03b1bfc63c606e427e.mp4?t=1596293150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
